 100:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****     *** Interrupt mode or DMA mode IO sequential operation ***
 101:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****     ==========================================================
 102:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****     [..]
 103:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (@) These interfaces allow to manage a sequential transfer with a repeated start condition
 104:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****           when a direction change during transfer
 105:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****     [..]
 106:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) A specific option field manage the different steps of a sequential transfer
 107:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) Option field values are defined through I2C_XFEROPTIONS and are listed below:
 108:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_FIRST_AND_LAST_FRAME: No sequential usage, functional is same as associated interfac
 109:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****            no sequential mode
 110:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_FIRST_FRAME: Sequential usage, this option allow to manage a sequence with start con
 111:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             and data to transfer without a final stop condition
 112:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_FIRST_AND_NEXT_FRAME: Sequential usage (Master only), this option allow to manage a 
 113:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             start condition, address and data to transfer without a final stop cond
 114:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             an then permit a call the same master sequential interface several time
 115:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             (like HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_IT() then HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit
 116:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             or HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_DMA() then HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_D
 117:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_NEXT_FRAME: Sequential usage, this option allow to manage a sequence with a restart 
 118:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             and with new data to transfer if the direction change or manage only th
 119:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             transfer
 120:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             if no direction change and without a final stop condition in both cases
 121:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_LAST_FRAME: Sequential usage, this option allow to manage a sequance with a restart 
 122:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             and with new data to transfer if the direction change or manage only th
 123:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             transfer
 124:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             if no direction change and with a final stop condition in both cases
 125:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_LAST_FRAME_NO_STOP: Sequential usage (Master only), this option allow to manage a re
 126:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             after several call of the same master sequential interface several time
