 297:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****      examples HAL_I2C_MasterTxCpltCallback(), HAL_I2C_MasterRxCpltCallback().
 298:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****      Exception done for MspInit and MspDeInit functions that are
 299:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****      reset to the legacy weak functions in the HAL_I2C_Init()/ HAL_I2C_DeInit() only when
