 512:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c **** 
 513:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) User must Implement HAL_I2C_MspInit() function in which he configures
 514:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****           all related peripherals resources (CLOCK, GPIO, DMA, IT and NVIC ).
