 516:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) Call the function HAL_I2C_Init() to configure the selected device with
 517:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****           the selected configuration:
 518:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****         (++) Clock Timing
 519:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****         (++) Own Address 1
