1052:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****     (#) There are two modes of transfer:
1053:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****        (++) Blocking mode : The communication is performed in the polling mode.
1054:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****             The status of all data processing is returned by the same function
1055:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****             after finishing transfer.
1056:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****        (++) No-Blocking mode : The communication is performed using Interrupts
1057:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****             or DMA. These functions return the status of the transfer startup.
1058:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****             The end of the data processing will be indicated through the
1059:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****             dedicated I2C IRQ when using Interrupt mode or the DMA IRQ when
1060:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****             using DMA mode.
1061:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c **** 
1062:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****     (#) Blocking mode functions are :
1063:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****         (++) HAL_I2C_Master_Transmit()
1064:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****         (++) HAL_I2C_Master_Receive()
1065:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****         (++) HAL_I2C_Slave_Transmit()
1066:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****         (++) HAL_I2C_Slave_Receive()
1067:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****         (++) HAL_I2C_Mem_Write()
1068:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****         (++) HAL_I2C_Mem_Read()
